  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HandlerContextAware, ReadLimitInfo, MaterialsDescriptionProvider, S3DataSource, SSEAwsKeyManagementParamsProvider, SSECustomerKeyProvider, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class UploadObjectRequest
extends AbstractPutObjectRequest
implements MaterialsDescriptionProvider, Serializable
    Used to request the client-side encryption and upload of a large S3 object via pipelined parallel multi-part uploads.
    See Also:
    AmazonS3EncryptionClient.uploadObject(UploadObjectRequest), Serialized Form
